videos.description: With under 30 seconds left, Wayne Selden Jr. dashes into the lane for the layup, but Kentucky's Jamal Murray gets all-ball on the block so strongly it sends Selden to the ground.
videos.headline: Murray's hellacious block sends Selden to the floor

videos.description: Kansas' Wayne Selden Jr. goes around the defender and throws down the huge dunk right in Skal Labissiere's face to give the Jayhawks the lead in overtime.
videos.headline: Overtime is dunk-time for Selden

videos.description: Wayne Selden Jr. Postgame Interview
videos.headline: Wayne Selden Jr. Postgame Interview

videos.description: Dan Shulman and Jay Bilas saw a classic game between legendary programs that came down to Wayne Selden taking over to lead the Jayhawks to the win.
videos.headline: Selden comes up huge for Kansas' OT win
